01:03:36.500 --> 01:03:38.060
[I told you it's not like that!]

01:03:38.060 --> 01:03:39.820
[You have to push it all the way!]

01:03:40.240 --> 01:03:41.380
Push it all the way, to your elbows.

01:03:41.380 --> 01:03:42.180
[The work is handed over from the scolding master]

01:03:42.180 --> 01:03:43.490
I'll do it.

01:03:43.490 --> 01:03:44.920
There's nothing I can do.

01:03:45.140 --> 01:03:46.420
[Small steps]

01:03:46.460 --> 01:03:48.620
[The cooled chicken]

01:03:51.860 --> 01:03:54.860
[Lifting a large basin as big as her own body]

01:03:55.300 --> 01:03:57.700
