-Some of those chicken bones are quite sharp. -Okay.

01:04:01.420 --> 01:04:04.260
[Yoon Namno: Some of those chicken bones
are quite sharp.]

01:04:04.300 --> 01:04:04.900
-The drumstick part. -Okay.

01:04:04.900 --> 01:04:05.070
[Yoon Namno: It really hurts if you get poked.]

01:04:05.070 --> 01:04:07.010
-It really hurts if you get poked. -Okay.

01:04:07.010 --> 01:04:07.460
-There can't be a single bone left. -I'll do it carefully.

01:04:07.460 --> 01:04:09.100
[Meticulous]
[I'll do it carefully!]

01:04:09.670 --> 01:04:09.860
-There can't be any bones. Not a single one. -Okay.

01:04:09.860 --> 01:04:11.940
[Repeatedly warning]
[Yoon Namno: There can't be any bones.
Not a single one!]

01:04:12.660 --> 01:04:16.860
[Separating the cooked meat from the bone]

01:04:17.140 --> 01:04:18.750
[Chef, no cartilage either, right?]

01:04:18.750 --> 01:04:19.660
No cartilage either.

01:04:19.660 --> 01:04:19.750
[Chef, I don't need to shred the chicken breast
into small pieces, right?]

01:04:19.750 --> 01:04:21.040
-Chef. -Here.

01:04:21.040 --> 01:04:23.930
I don't need to shred the chicken breast
into tiny bits, right? Should I?

01:04:23.930 --> 01:04:24.560
Shred it.

01:04:24.560 --> 01:04:25.540
-I mean... -Okay.

01:04:25.540 --> 01:04:28.060
-Just shred it a little bit. -Okay.

01:04:28.980 --> 01:04:32.380
[Eyes never wavering]
[Focus mode]

01:04:34.140 --> 01:04:36.780
