01:04:40.140 --> 01:04:40.920
[Warm]

01:04:40.920 --> 01:04:41.990
It's cooled down a lot now.

01:04:41.990 --> 01:04:43.680
Yeah, you have to let it cool.

01:04:43.680 --> 01:04:44.540
-The chicken isn't too dry, right? It's just right. -Yeah.

01:04:44.540 --> 01:04:46.980
[Chicken cooked to perfection]

01:04:47.980 --> 01:04:50.140
