01:05:16.980 --> 01:05:18.340
[Hong Jinkyung: She has too many fans. I can't.]

01:05:18.340 --> 01:05:19.260
It's okay.

01:05:19.260 --> 01:05:19.340
It's already passed 9 million.

01:05:19.340 --> 01:05:21.060
[Haha]

01:05:21.380 --> 01:05:22.460
[It passed 10 million. 10 million.]

01:05:22.460 --> 01:05:23.370
[Startled]
[Really...? Over 10 million?]

01:05:23.370 --> 01:05:24.970
-Over 10 million? -Yes.

01:05:24.970 --> 01:05:25.180
-Over 10 million?

01:05:25.180 --> 01:05:26.590
[As of the broadcast date,
she has approximately 11.7 million followers]

01:05:26.590 --> 01:05:27.590
-Yeah. -Yes.

01:05:27.660 --> 01:05:29.650
[Hong Jinkyung: Younjung, let's take a selfie later.]

01:05:29.650 --> 01:05:29.820
