01:06:09.500 --> 01:06:11.140
[Park Myungsoo: Jinkyung, because you're ugly...]

01:06:11.180 --> 01:06:12.870
[Are there any inconvenient things
because you're ugly?]

01:06:12.870 --> 01:06:14.240
Jinkyung.

01:06:15.050 --> 01:06:15.060
Jinkyung.

01:06:15.060 --> 01:06:16.070
[You reap what you sow]

01:06:16.070 --> 01:06:17.180
Are there any inconvenient things because you're ugly?

01:06:17.180 --> 01:06:18.240
Come on, say something.

01:06:18.240 --> 01:06:20.210
So annoying.

01:06:20.210 --> 01:06:20.740
-You're ugly... -My body is tired enough as it is.

01:06:20.740 --> 01:06:22.940
[Hong Jinkyung: My body is tired enough as it is.]

01:06:22.940 --> 01:06:25.080
