01:07:52.520 --> 01:07:54.000
Cut the octopus into strips.

01:07:54.000 --> 01:07:54.690
OK.

01:07:54.690 --> 01:07:56.620
I'll go cut the octopus. This is fun.

01:07:56.620 --> 01:07:57.060
