01:07:57.060 --> 01:07:58.290
I'll cut it.

01:08:07.760 --> 01:08:09.570
It's cooked perfectly.

01:08:10.860 --> 01:08:12.060
[Need to cut red peppers! Red peppers!]

01:08:15.580 --> 01:08:19.020
[Seafood Knife-Cut Noodles: Clean chicken, then simmer,
make broth, prepare octopus & veggie garnish,
