01:08:19.500 --> 01:08:23.340
[Because there are lots of tiny bones]
[The chicken prep is also nearing the end!]

01:08:23.620 --> 01:08:26.040
[Wow, I've got eagle eyes. Admit it, right?]

01:08:26.040 --> 01:08:27.460
-See that? -I've got eagle eyes. Admit it.

01:08:27.460 --> 01:08:28.700
[Admitted]

01:08:31.569 --> 01:08:32.740
Give it to me. I'll cut it.

01:08:32.740 --> 01:08:36.180
[Seafood Knife-Cut Noodles: Clean chicken, then simmer,
make broth, prepare octopus & veggie garnish,
debone chicken, knife-cut noodles.]

01:08:36.540 --> 01:08:37.979
[Accelerating]

01:08:39.620 --> 01:08:41.979
[Decisive knife work]

01:08:42.580 --> 01:08:46.300
[Flawless neatness]

01:08:51.899 --> 01:09:03.899
[Preparing Seafood Knife-Cut Noodles]

01:09:03.899 --> 01:09:08.020
[Fire station late-night snacks prep: Seafood Knife-Cut Noodles,
