That's it.

01:09:12.430 --> 01:09:13.960
-Thanks. -Good job.

01:09:13.960 --> 01:09:15.340
-Thanks. -Good job.

01:09:15.340 --> 01:09:17.260
[Finally]

01:09:17.260 --> 01:09:19.149
-Good job. -Good job.

01:09:19.149 --> 01:09:20.390
