01:10:42.980 --> 01:10:43.870
[Park Myungsoo: We must happily enjoy it.]

01:10:43.870 --> 01:10:45.460
-Thank you. -Thank you.

01:10:45.460 --> 01:10:46.660
-Hae-in, thank you.

01:10:46.660 --> 01:10:47.480
[Help yourselves!]

01:10:47.480 --> 01:10:49.460
Hae-in, thank you. You'll be more and more famous.

01:10:49.460 --> 01:10:51.060
Everything Jung Hae-in bought is delicious.

01:10:51.060 --> 01:10:51.740
Thank you.

01:10:51.740 --> 01:10:53.120
The Tteokbokki is delicious.

01:10:53.120 --> 01:10:54.390
Delicious.

01:10:54.660 --> 01:10:59.180
[Food tastes better after people work hard]

01:10:59.720 --> 01:11:00.580
The Tteokbokki is delicious.

01:11:00.580 --> 01:11:01.540
[Yum!]

01:11:02.780 --> 01:11:04.200
[Hong Jinkyung: Looks like we're doing our jobs fast.]

01:11:04.200 --> 01:11:05.560
[That's why we have time to eat here.]

